  "Vellynne Harpell\nMedium humanoid (Human), neutral\nArmor Class 13 (bracers of defense)\nHit Points 67 (9d8 + 27)\nSpeed run 20 ft.\nSTR 10 (+0)\nDEX 12 (+1)\nCON 17 (+3)\nINT 18 (+4)\nWIS 15 (+2)\nCHA 13 (+1)\nSaving Throws Int +6, Wis +4\nSkills Arcana +6, History +6\nSenses passive Perception 12\nLanguages Common, Draconic, Dwarvish, Elvish, Orc\nChallenge 4 (1100 XP)\nSpecial Equipment.\nSpellcasting.\nActions\nVampiric Touch (3rd-Level Spell; Requieres a Spell Slot).\nChill Touch (Cantrip).\nWand of Magic Missiles.\nThis full creature's stat block is not available (not OGL).\n\nVellynne Harpell is a necromancer from the famous Harpell family of Longsaddle.\nAdventures (Rime of the Frostmaiden)",
